{"title":"如何给网站备案。","uid":"fb302340c224de8c977c94c48c27091d","slug":"域名备案","date":"2021-09-29T12:03:25.000Z","updated":"2021-10-04T11:10:33.006Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/域名备案.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://p.qlogo.cn/zc_icon/0/2cd397c5338df4516ea765030ad6b8d916329174161791/0.png","content":"<h2 id=\"域名备案\"><a href=\"#域名备案\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"域名备案\"></a><center>域名备案</h2><p> 今天又买了一个域名，sociawork.cn 顺道去看看备案要求(–是不可能–，这辈子都不可能–)。</p>\n<p> 哇 可以写成书的要求，</p>\n<p> <img src=\"https://p.qlogo.cn/zc_icon/0/2a7088eaecb4d69d5bb800e86d3e6c751632917391503/0.jpg\" alt=\"img_0033.jpg\"></p>\n<p>废话不多说了，来学习一下如何给网站备案。</p>\n<p>我看过的大部分个人备案过的博客都不符合要求。因为他们只进行了ICP备案，同时有ICP备和公安网备的极少。</p>\n<p>本文的重点是谈一谈，服务器在国外要不要备案。直接看我们之所以要备案的法规：<a href=\"https://beian.miit.gov.cn/#/Integrated/lawStatute\">非经营性互联网信息服务备案管理办法</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://p.qlogo.cn/zc_icon/0/07901695c5629f3b09aecb45b96b2d8016329177692107/0.png\" alt=\"1.png\"></p>\n<p>看完了吧。有没有疑惑啊？</p>\n<p>我有疑惑，就是这条法规或者整个备案管理办法有区分你de服务器是在国内还是国外吗？或者说整个法规有涉及到服务器的概念吗？？？？</p>\n<p>让我们把这条法规再读一遍。</p>\n<p> 组织或个人利用通过<font size=\"40\">互联网域名</font> 访问的网站或者利用仅能通过<font size=\"40\">互联网IP地址</font>访问的网站，提供非经营性互联网信息服务。</p>\n<hr>\n\n<p>还不明白的我举个例子：比如法律规定不能放火。然后下面的人说用打火机可以用火柴不可以。但我看到的规定是不能放火，整个规定都没有涉及打火机或者火柴的概念。<br>就是这个意思。</p>\n<p>再回过头看非经营性互联网信息服务备案管理办法，整个办法都没有涉及<code>服务器</code>或者是<code>哪里的服务器</code>的概念。所以，国外服务器不要备案依据的法律条文在哪？</p>\n<p>不明白我意思的再读一遍。或者说把国外服务器无需备案的具体法律条文给我看看。<br>最后，再复习一下：</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>AI朗读：</p></blockquote>\n<audio controls=\"controls\" preload=\"meta\" src=\"https://pan.bilnn.com/api/v3/file/sourcejump/814Eo7FW/wMRY418C63JV73qAopow1XEft6GYyodBtdD03Vo5vmE*\" >\nYour browser does not support the audio element.\n</audio>\n\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>自己看</p></blockquote>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=